1. Create a ticket title to fit the issue.
2. Create the description based on the issue with the following structure:

Bug/Feature

Enviroment (e.g. Live)

System (e.g. Laravel v11.x)

Affected Components

Specification

Code Examples

Expected Result

Hints/Risks

Attachments

4. Create the ticket as a markdown file in docs/tickets.
5. Create a detailed plan based on your analysis and the ticket as a markdown file in docs/plans.

Just create the ticket and the plan. Do not start with the implementation.